fullplot: Would-be superhero, Ed Gruberman, who possesses no super powers must join a team of misfit heroes-in-training known as The Super Capers. Having only faith, Gruberman must travel through time to uncover an evil plot involving some gold bullion, a fiery femme fatale, and a criminal mastermind with a dark secret about Ed's past.
plot: A good guy with no powers joins a superhero team with no clue against a bad guy with no shame.
title: Super Capers: The Origins of Ed and the Missing Bullion
